@Xcode 

The topic of DACs and Guilds has come up again. During internal discussions, several Star Atlas oriented business have posed whether or not the DAC platform will have sufficient ability to differentiate to the public between Gameplay focused DACs and Business focused DACs (not that either are mutually exclusive) - but the concern exists amongst both ATMTA and the general public on how we best handle the desired neutrality of Business DACs. 

Would it be possible to do an AMA or have a small group discussion on the matter?

One of the things that I like more in games… is to find out in game playing what I can do inside of the game!! That’s why it’s call A Game…

@SW4GN3R @bunthius and jake!! Plus team … enjoy your weekend and thanks for keeping our dream alive !!! 
Cheers
